{"tid":953644,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"王祖賢近照 🙄","createTime":"2018-12-24T05:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T18:07:51.000Z","uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cce6df93fa6c1988d041fdc72903e38ce0f55d2d","tid":953644,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T05:52:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">撇身材走樣王祖賢近照瘦了 加拿大豪宅意外曝光</span><br />\n<br />\n「永遠的小倩」王祖賢息影後，就定居加拿大潛心修佛，不過偶爾仍會透過社群，和粉絲分享近況，近日她的粉絲會微博曬出2張她的近照，狀態看起來相當好的她，一雙長腿相當吸睛，而網友也發現，照片背景疑似是她加拿大的家，引起熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-12-23/656/20181223001251.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-12-23%2F656%2F20181223001251.jpg&h=bc876e8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前幾年佢黎個樣唔係唔同左咩 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8996882772cec60b6deadaa4bf900f726f2a9aaa","tid":953644,"uid":5236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T05:53:46.000Z","msg":"似三十頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d13641dd56a722d61ce5012417342ef6927cd2c3","tid":953644,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T05:54:47.000Z","msg":"王祖賢日前被曝光她在加拿大吃火鍋照片，不過卻看起來嚴重駝背，且水桶腰明顯，讓網友驚嘆「女神真的老了」，不過22日，她的粉絲會微博曝光2張她的近照，並祝大家「聖誕快樂」，照片中她帶著灰色毛帽，穿上毛衣搭牛仔褲，看起來狀態維持相當好，尖下巴和一雙長腿相當吸睛，氣質依舊宛如少女，根本不像51歲，令人驚艷不已。<br />\n<br />\n網友大讚她「簡直亞洲腿神」，並誇她依舊美「這是什麼神仙姐姐」，也有人發現她照片背景似是她加拿大豪宅，佈置以白色為主軸，還有個小暖爐，看起來溫馨又典雅。<br />\n<br />\n(中時電子報)"},{"pid":"121bf743d6f0e91ce9156a975693b420398e0dc2","tid":953644,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T05:55:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-12-23/360/20181223001255.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-12-23%2F360%2F20181223001255.jpg&h=d32f61d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n王祖賢之前被拍到身材走樣。"},{"pid":"b8e438e678ccee71032f33b2f3665eabad913063","tid":953644,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T05:55:54.000Z","msg":"人地影vs自己影=.="},{"pid":"bc254ee738d3444f0f9250a5fc605d5d913ee3b5","tid":953644,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T05:57:26.000Z","msg":"世事往往就係咁簡單=.=&quot;"},{"pid":"05e2d1ae2411056643d420719a7bae0df862bbae","tid":953644,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T06:00:03.000Z","msg":"睇錯王祖藍。。。。。。"},{"pid":"ef45bbd7f5be9806cedad739a45a9962841643c4","tid":953644,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T06:21:48.000Z","msg":"推薦三套佢同學友拍既片 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png&h=f99a10a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9yARvPjN4s4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9yARvPjN4s4&d=TQx6GH%2FuAz9pcikEHCQ2%2BJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=4c61a38b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9yARvPjN4s4</a><br />\n夢過界 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VFhG-BY_nNo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVFhG-BY_nNo&d=TQx6GH%2FuAz9pcikEHCQ2%2BJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=4a9d31eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VFhG-BY_nNo</a><br />\n都市煞星<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KhqjB5cIRgc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKhqjB5cIRgc&d=TQx6GH%2FuAz9pcikEHCQ2%2BJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=db93bfd5\" target=\"_bl